st: day of pentecost
st: _Whitsunday_
tb: Almighty God, on this day, through the outpouring of the Holy Spirit, you revealed the way of
    eternal life to every race and nation: Pour out this gift anew, that by the preaching of the
    Gospel your salvation may reach to the ends of the earth; through Jesus Christ our Lord, who
    lives and reigns with you, in the unity of the Holy Spirit, one God, for ever and ever.
    **Amen.**
